{"tid":370081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾200人報案稱遭假活佛騙財","createTime":"2017-08-22T21:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T01:24:44.000Z","uid":37554,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"31c321775649fc092af0192bb5fdc72ca56ff8a1","tid":370081,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T21:29:48.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】超過200人到灣仔警察總部請願及報案，他們報稱被一名自稱活佛的人詐騙，涉及總金額超過八千萬元。<br />\n<br />\n二百多人包括部分來自內地及台灣，他們手持橫額及標語遊行到灣仔警察總部報案。他們報稱被一名自稱活佛的香港人陳寶生詐騙財產，部分人損失過百萬元，亦有人指遭到性侵犯。他們遞交請願信，逐一到警署報案。<br />\n<br />\n協助他們的立法會議員劉國勳表示，至今有近600人報稱被詐騙，涉及超過八千萬元。"},{"pid":"b9e16edaafc052f0b04cc30ed5bfc2ae387a665f","tid":370081,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T21:30:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=233126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D233126&d=wdi%2FwlnpTPpwbaPXYtwCwP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=c104b966\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D233126&h=85b02062\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=233126</a>"},{"pid":"78b46a4bc9ff34d1cc247e120f72cb181c1cb892","tid":370081,"uid":5218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T21:37:01.000Z","msg":"比活佛性侵？！係咪一路𨳒一路念喃嘸咁有聲有畫面？"},{"pid":"fd33c4c53f6990fb32a5ed5544caf417d61b111f","tid":370081,"uid":36010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T21:38:01.000Z","msg":"俾老衲條撚屌呃咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c1f2a131e948806b3dd3e16778b30f13b5e061","tid":370081,"uid":131621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T21:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb8d50ed5301f7c578f8c17902b647f00025615","tid":370081,"uid":45290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-